3.text: Long sait bilong edukesen, planti lain i bin toktok long dispela websait.

4.text: Ol 'tour' i go long dispela hap em i no bikpela mani long ol bikpela grup, olsem na sapos yu go yu yet o wantaim wanpela pren, traim long bungim ol narapela manmeri na kamapim wanpela grup we o gat foapela o sikspela lain long kisim wanpela gutpela reit (rate).

5.text: Sampela 'medium‑format' film kamera i save yusim wanpela '6 by 6 cm' fomet, tru tru em i '56 by 56 mm' negatif.

6.text: Mekim na karim kopi bilong ol polisi bilong yu na kontek infomesen bilong 'insurer' bilong yu wantaim yu.

7.text: Pulapim haus bilong yu wantaim wanpela naispela kofi long moning na sampela 'chamomile' ti bilong rileks (relax) long nait.

8.text: Ol 'avalanche' em ol i no samting we i no nomol; ol sap maunten i ken holim sampela sno tasol, moa sno bai kam daun olsem 'avalanche'.

9.text: Straksa bilong 'income tax' em i narakain long narapela narapela kantri, na reit (rate) bilong takis na 'brackets' em i narakain narakain long wanwan kantri.
